ces</label></div><div class="form-radio"><input class="form-check-input form-select-search radio-target" data-autoclose="true" id="searchField-input-TRAVAUX_PREP" value="TRAVAUX_PREP" type="radio" name="searchField" onclick="validateTroncatureSearchAdvancesSltChmp(&#39;select-target-group&#39;,&#39;&#39;,&#39;TRAVAUX_PREP&#39;,&#39;true&#39;)"/><label class="form-check-label" for="searchField-input-TRAVAUX_PREP">Dans les travaux préparatoires</label></div><div class="form-radio"><input class="form-check-input form-select-search radio-target" data-autoclose="true" id="searchField-input-SIGNATURE" value="SIGNATURE" type="radio" name="searchField" onclick="validateTroncatureSearchAdvancesSltChmp(&#39;select-target-group&#39;,&#39;&#39;,&#39;SIGNATURE&#39;,&#39;true&#39;)"/><label class="form-check-label" for="searchField-input-SIGNATURE">Dans les signatures</label></div><div class="form-radio"><input class="form-check-input form-select-search radio-target" data-autoclose="true" id="searchField-input-NOTA" value="NOTA" type="radio" name="searchField" onclick="validateTroncatureSearchAdvancesSltChmp(&#39;select-target-group&#39;,&#39;&#39;,&#39;NOTA&#39;,&#39;true&#39;)"/><label class="form-check-label" for="searchField-input-NOTA">Dans les notas</label></div><div class="form-radio"><input class="form-check-input form-select-search radio-target" data-autoclose="true" id="searchField-input-NUM_AFFAIRE" value="NUM_AFFAIRE" type="radio" name="searchField" onclick="validateTroncatureSearchAdvancesSltChmp(&#39;select-target-group&#39;,&#39;&#39;,&#39;NUM_AFFAIRE&#39;,&#39;true&#39;)"/><label class="form-check-label" for="searchField-input-NUM_AFFAIRE">Dans les numéros d’affaires</label></div><div class="form-radio"><input class="form-check-input form-select-search radio-target" data-autoclose="true" id="searchField-input-ABSTRATS" value="ABSTRATS" type="radio" name="searchField" onclick="validateTroncatureSearchAdvancesSltChmp(&#39;select-target-group&#39;,&#39;&#39;,&#39;ABS